u2013\n|clubs10             = [[Manisa FK]]\n|caps10              = 16\n|goals10             = 9\n|totalcaps           = \n|totalgoals          = \n|nationalyears1      = 2013\n|nationalteam1       = [[Turkey national under-20 football team|Turkey U20]]\n|nationalcaps1       = 2\n|nationalgoals1      = 0\n|medaltemplates      = \n|club-update         = 20:15, 12 May 2019 (UTC)\n|nationalteam-update = \n}}\n'''Sinan Kurumu\u015f''' (born 2 August 1994) is a Turkish [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]] for [[Manisa FK]]. He made his [[S\u00fcper Lig]] debut for [[MKE Ankarag\u00fcc\u00fc|Ankarag\u00fcc\u00fc]] on 18 February 2012.{{Citation needed|date=April 2014}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.tff.org/Default.aspx?pageId=526&kisiId=950263 Player profile] at TFF.org\n* [https://int.soccerway.com/players/sinan-kurumu/230354/ Sinan Kurumu\u015f] at Soccerway\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kurumus, Sinan}}\n[[Category:1994 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from \u0130neg\u00f6l]]\n[[Category:Turkish footballers]]\n[[Category:Turkey youth international footballers]]\n[[Category:MKE Ankarag\u00fcc\u00fc footballers]]\n[[Category:Be\u015fikta\u015f J.K. footballers]]\n[[Category:Boluspor footballers]]\n[[Category:S\u00fcper Lig players]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n\n\n{{Turkey-footy-forward-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Multiple issues|\n{{BLP sources|date=April 2014}}\n{{one source|date=April 2014}}\n}}\n\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name                = Sinan Kurumu\u015f\n|image               = \n|caption             = \n|fullname            = Sinan Kurumu\u015f\n|birth_date          = {{birth date and age|1994|08|02|df=y}}\n|birth_place         = [[\u0130neg\u00f6l]], Turkey\n|height              = {{convert|1.87|m|ftin|0|abbr=on}}\n|position            = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n|currentclub         = Manisa FK\n|clubnumber        